{"word":"ἀκροάομαι","slug":"ἀκροάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκροάομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:derived, derivation'>Deriv.</a> uncertain.\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hearken to, listen to</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to listen</i>, <el>ὁ ἀκροώμενος</el> <i>a hearer, disciple</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to attend to, obey</i>, <el>τινός</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}